data.description: Acreage & square footage in Oconee County.There's so much more than that in this 5+acre property snugly situated on Watson Springs Rd!The house sits slightly off the road & through some lush trees,adding extra privacy.Huge front porch & back deck allows for maximum outdoors enjoyment.Inside,there's plenty of room for growing or large families,w/large open kitchen,& equally open great room.There's also the master suite,mudroom/laundry room combo & an extra family room/office space on the main level.Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms,2 w/large walk-in closets,& an extra family space to create adult-child separation (if you want it).Throw in a new high-efficiency,16-seer heat pump w/transferable warranty,& you have tranquil living in a superb location
